%N A397217 Decimal expansion of imaginary part (Pi/3)*Integral_{x>=0} log(1/2+i*x)^3/cosh(Pi*x)^2 dx.
%C A397217 Let f(n) = -(Pi/(n+1))*Integral_{x>=0} log(1/2+i*x)^(n+1)/cosh(Pi*x)^2 dx then f(n) = gamma_n + alpha_n, where gamma_n is n-th Stieltjes constant and alpha_n is n-th alpha new constant.
%C A397217 This constant equals -alpha_2.
%e A397217 0.05396938027501910571839699868...
%o A397217 (PARI) imag( -(Pi/3)*intnum(x=0, [oo, 2*Pi], log(1/2+I*x)^3/cosh(Pi*x)^2))
%Y A397217 Cf. A086279, A397095, A397154.
%K A397217 nonn,cons
%O A397217 0,2
